OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FTwenty-five intelligence experts and
OL,7,Ffour special forces crew were killed
OL,8,Fwhen the helicopter crashed on the
OL,9,FMull of Kintyre, en route from RAF
OL,10,FAldergrove in Northern Ireland to Fort
OL,11,FGeorge near Inverness, in June 1994.
OL,13,FThe incident was initially blamed on
OL,14,Fpilot error before this was overturned
OL,15,Fin 2011.
OL,17,FFamilies of the victims are calling
OL,18,Ffor a judge-led public inquiry into
OL,19,Fthe disaster and for all the files `
OL,20,Fsome of which have been sealed for 100
OL,21,Fyears ` to be released.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FThe Chinook Justice Campaign group has
OL,7,Falso said that newly released Ministry
OL,8,Fof Defence (MoD) documents show
OL,9,Fofficials were aware of serious
OL,10,Fairworthiness concerns about the
OL,11,Fhelicopter, while actively seeking to
OL,12,Fprotect the official narrative blaming
OL,13,Fthe pilots.
OL,15,FOn Saturday, relatives of those who
OL,16,Fdied in the 1994 crash laid wreaths at
OL,17,Fthe Memorial Garden at Thiepval
OL,18,FBarracks, Lisburn, ahead of the 32nd
OL,19,Fanniversary of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FDes and Patricia Conroy lost their
OL,7,Ffather Desmond, a detective chief
OL,8,Fsuperintendent in the Royal Ulster
OL,9,FConstabulary (RUC) who died in the
OL,10,Fcrash.
OL,12,FMr Conroy said "it's quite obvious
OL,13,Fthat there were issues with the
OL,14,Faircraft all the way back to 1994 and
OL,15,Fthe aircraft should never have taken
OL,16,Foff", and a "judge-led public inquiry
OL,17,Fis all that can come of this now".
OL,19,F"The truth is being withheld," he said.
OL,26,@tD@POUxD@DO]xD@MOUyD@aO]{D@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,F"We want justice, we want an apology
OL,7,Ffrom the Government that our loved
OL,8,Fones were placed on an aircraft that
OL,9,Fwasn't released for service.
OL,11,F"The MoD, the RAF themselves, it
OL,12,Fwasn't to be relied upon in any way
OL,13,Fwhatsoever.
OL,15,F"I want to fight for my father,
OL,16,Fbecause I believe if he knew the
OL,17,Faircraft was in the condition it was
OL,18,Fin, he would not have boarded the
OL,19,Faircraft, nor would his colleagues."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
