PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FHe added: "My father taught me to do
OL,7,Fthe right thing, that's all I can
OL,8,Fremember, no matter how difficult it
OL,9,Fis, always try to do the right thing.
OL,11,F"And that's what I'm going to try and
OL,12,Fdo for him, is to try and get justice
OL,13,Ffor him and I believe the people who
OL,14,Fknow the answers should do the right
OL,15,Fthing."
OL,17,FMs Conroy, who was 22 years old when
OL,18,Fher father died, described him as "a
OL,19,Floving husband, family man".
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUwD@GO]zD@cOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
