OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,F"He was hard working, he was honest,
OL,7,Fhe took us away on picnics and
OL,8,Fholidays, he just loved being at
OL,9,Fhome," she said.
OL,11,F"So when that happened, the centre of
OL,12,Four universe was just like it was just
OL,13,Fripped apart."
OL,15,FShe said the wreath laying ceremony
OL,16,Fwas "extremely emotional", and nearly
OL,17,F32 years on the families of the
OL,18,Fvictims "take great comfort in each
OL,19,Fother".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]sD@AOUuD@NO]xD@EOUxD@YO]zD@
OL,26,AIOU{D@FO]
