OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FLast month, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer said he would meet with the
OL,8,Ffamilies after the case was raised in
OL,9,Fthe Commons.
OL,11,F"We are ready, we want to meet him, we
OL,12,Fwant him to meet us, to listen to us,
OL,13,Fto take what we have to say seriously,
OL,14,Fto our evidence to be looked at," Ms
OL,15,FConroy said.
OL,17,FJennifer Balmer-Hornby lost her
OL,18,Ffather, Major Anthony Robert Hornby,
OL,19,Fwith the accident occurring a week
OL,20,Fbefore her 10th birthday.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FMs Balmer-Hornby said a full public
OL,7,Finquiry is important to the families
OL,8,Fbecause they feel "there's more
OL,9,Finformation out there, but they are
OL,10,Flocking it away".
OL,12,F"We've had inquiries already, all the
OL,13,Finquiries have been about the cause of
OL,14,Fthe crash," she said.
OL,26,@pD@SOUrD@PO]tD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,F"This is not about the cause of the
OL,7,Fcrash. It's about the mountain of
OL,8,Fevidence to say that that aircraft
OL,9,Fshould never have taken off, and why
OL,10,Fwould they risk the lives of 29 people
OL,11,Fwho were so crucial to the security of
OL,12,Fthis country?"
OL,14,FMs Eastwood said those who remember
OL,15,Fthe incident also "remember the
OL,16,Fsilence that accompanied afterwards,
OL,17,Fthe useful conspiracy theories that
OL,18,Ffell into that vacuum due to a lack of
OL,19,Finformation and facts".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]wD@SOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,F"The tragedy, now 32 years on, is that
OL,7,Fthe Government are still trying to
OL,8,Fcover this up and telling families
OL,9,Fbare face lies that these need to be
OL,10,Fcovered up for 100 years ` the files `
OL,11,Fthat's not true," she said.
OL,13,F"And it suits some individuals to have
OL,14,Fconspiracy theories out there.
OL,16,F"It's not the truth, it's hurtful to
OL,17,Fthe families, and actually every time
OL,18,Fthey tell their stories and they share
OL,19,Ftheir stories, they are re-
OL,20,Ftraumatising themselves."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]uD@AOUxD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough Law, formally known
OL,7,Fas the Public Office (Accountability)
OL,8,FBill, was carried over from the last
OL,9,Fparliamentary session, and will
OL,10,Frequire public officials to tell the
OL,11,Ftruth during inquiries and
OL,12,Finvestigations.
OL,14,FMs Eastwood said: "We really need to
OL,15,Fsee that Hillsborough law delivered
OL,16,Fnow, and it's urgent, and this can
OL,17,Fserve as a test case."
OL,26,@vD@SOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FShe added: "The Hillsborough law
OL,7,Fitself is to do with the duty of
OL,8,Fcandour, and what that means is
OL,9,Fgovernment bodies and public bodies
OL,10,Ftelling the truth, the whole truth,
OL,11,Fand nothing but the truth.
OL,26,@nD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,F"That is exactly what these families
OL,7,Fare calling for what all the
OL,8,Finformation the families have amassed
OL,9,Fsays and tells us, and this is an
OL,10,Fopportunity for the Government, if
OL,11,Fthey are serious about public
OL,12,Faccountability and about duty of
OL,13,Fcandour, this provides the ideal
OL,14,Fopportunity for this to be used for
OL,15,Fthe families to actually get the truth
OL,16,Fof what happened, because they haven't
OL,17,Fyet."
OL,19,FThe Alliance MP further said the
OL,20,FGovernment has "failed" the crash
OL,21,Fvictims and their families.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@EO]|D@POU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
