FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,FShe added: "Not only failed them, but
OL,7,Fthen covered it up and told them they
OL,8,Fwere liars, and that's why this case
OL,9,Fis so important, because none of these
OL,10,Fpeople are liars, their families were
OL,11,Fheroes, and the state needs to, at the
OL,12,Fvery least, give them the truth."
OL,14,FAn MoD spokesperson said: "Our
OL,15,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with
OL,16,Fthe families, friends, and colleagues
OL,17,Fof all those who died in the Mull of
OL,18,FKintyre crash.
OL,26,@nD@LOUtD@aO]vD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
