OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780326668
OL,3,CChinook families say truth being
OL,4,Cwithheld over 1994 disaster
OL,6,F"The MoD continues to engage with the
OL,7,FChinook Justice Campaign (CJC)
OL,8,Fthroughout this process.
OL,10,F"Defence ministers have met with
OL,11,Fcampaign representatives to listen to
OL,12,Ftheir concerns, and the CJC also met
OL,13,Fwith the Ministry of Justice victims
OL,14,Fminister in March.
OL,16,F"The CJC submitted a formal claim for
OL,17,FJudicial Review in September 2025, and
OL,18,Fthe MoD is focused on responding fully
OL,19,Fto that claim and to the allegations
OL,20,Fit contains.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/17
